{"tid":2233452,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[結婚巴絲入一入嚟] 搵婚禮Deco 小心黑店！","createTime":"2020-10-07T06:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T06:57:59.000Z","uid":36563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"000697f1c12dc3550fc46ea80275633b8912bfc2","tid":2233452,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"有個fd嚟緊結婚，上年已經搵咗間deco叫<strong><ins>L_ve Opti_n<br />\n</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n個Fd因為疫情要改期<br />\n點知比間deco公司話要收1000改期費，<br />\n新期係旺季仲要再收1000<br />\n但個plan都係一萬有找<br />\n<br />\n佢話佢另外啲攝影化妝花車公司，甚至其他deco都冇收呢啲疫情改期費用<br />\n後尾上網見到原來都有唔少人中咗伏寧願撻訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢見嚟緊又有婚展，想叫我幫佢開post提吓大家唔好中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外上網搵到有人開以下既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2019婚展時俾左decoration deposit </strong><br />\n<br />\n點知依家疫情咁嚴重，問有冇得extend，佈置公司話只可以半年內用，仲要比行政費用等雜費。 <br />\n但其實全世界都知疫情冇可能咁快停。 <br />\n<br />\n唉！信錯咗佢，講到話係連續幾次結婚展大會指定婚禮佈置公司，一啲人情味都冇，擺明R哂d錢。<br />\n<br />\n1)   如果客人取消婚禮或未能確定新日子，客人可以選擇取消訂單，會視為撻訂，所有已付款項一概不會退款。到客人有確定日子，客人可以以9折優惠價重新參加佈置套餐。<br />\n<br />\n2)   公司只接受*一次性*改期，改期時間為期big day半年之內，需要收返$1000行政費。如果新改期日子為九月至三月，要另付旺季特別附加費$1000。如果客人改期通知，最遲要兩個星期之前通知，少於兩星期通知，需$1000附加費。如果日子超過半年，公司有權收取另外附加費。建議客人提早通知我們，及按自己需要選擇日子。<br />\n如到big day 前2星期最後也夾不了日子，就會視為取消訂單，都不設退款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://wow.esdlife.com/space.php?uid=168615&amp;do=blog&amp;id=436990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwow.esdlife.com%2Fspace.php%3Fuid%3D168615%26do%3Dblog%26id%3D436990&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=8fecb0a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://wow.esdlife.com/space.php?uid=168615&amp;do=blog&amp;id=436990</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps 個fd係cd rom，得個netvigator email冇得開ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485c1c5e609a15549cc3e758a5124a9be93f4832","tid":2233452,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e05d3e03fe76c8fc1db809c600177e3815bf2a2","tid":2233452,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2ac83657673716b127c79bc9843d19e67a8a72","tid":2233452,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d2825ccaf0b4563eaa8f2f59f42a101a38d00f","tid":2233452,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"自推提點大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}